The account tile uses the [Flexicell](/components/flexi-cell) component.

When displaying a **savings** or **transaction account**, display the account name (or nickname), account balance and the account number details.

```tsx
<FlexiCell
  tag="a"
  href="#"
  withBorder
  after={
    <FlexiCellAdornment align="top">
      <FlexiCellLabel tag="h3" rightLabel>
        $9,999.99
      </FlexiCellLabel>
    </FlexiCellAdornment>
  }
>
  <FlexiCellLabel tag="h3">Account name</FlexiCellLabel>
  <FlexiCellHint>032-123 12345678</FlexiCellHint>
</FlexiCell>
```

When listing a **credit card,** **loan account** or **transaction account** with a **debit card,** display the account name (or nickname), account balance, available balance and the account number or masked card number details.

```tsx
<FlexiCell
  tag="a"
  href="#"
  withBorder
  after={
    <FlexiCellAdornment align="top">
      <FlexiCellLabel tag="h3" rightLabel>
        $9,999.99
      </FlexiCellLabel>
      <FlexiCellHint>avail $9,999.99</FlexiCellHint>
    </FlexiCellAdornment>
  }
>
  <FlexiCellLabel tag="h3">Credit card name</FlexiCellLabel>
  <FlexiCellHint>Card ending in 1234</FlexiCellHint>
</FlexiCell>
```
